            "text": "\n\n{\n  \"messages\": [\n    {\n      \"content\": \"Reply with one short sentence only.\",\n      \"additional_kwargs\": {},\n      \"response_metadata\": {},\n      \"id\": \"ef86e22f-bd01-4f56-9690-8443638133be\",\n      \"type\": \"human\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"content\": \"\",\n      \"additional_kwargs\": {\n        \"tool_calls\": [\n          {\n            \"index\": 0,\n            \"id\": \"call_zxs31OjxSYsNsT3PSwozW9FU\",\n            \"type\": \"function\",\n            \"function\": {\n              \"name\": \"load_skill\",\n              \"arguments\": \"{\\\"skillName\\\": \\\"retrieval-protocol\\\"}\"\n            }\n          },\n          {\n            \"index\": 1,\n            \"id\": \"call_fIxkLj7w5pbJUDvFyWl5W2is\",\n            \"type\": \"function\",\n            \"function\": {\n              \"name\": \"load_skill\",\n              \"arguments\": \"{\\\"skillName\\\": \\\"output-contract\\\"}\"\n            }\n          }\n        ]\n      },\n      \"response_metadata\": {\n        \"model_provider\": \"openai\",\n        \"usage\": {\n          \"prompt_tokens\": 469,\n          \"completion_tokens\": 53,\n          \"total_tokens\": 522,\n          \"prompt_tokens_details\": {\n            \"cached_tokens\": 0,\n            \"audio_tokens\": 0\n          },\n          \"completion_tokens_details\": {\n            \"reasoning_tokens\": 0,\n            \"audio_tokens\": 0,\n            \"accepted_prediction_tokens\": 0,\n            \"rejected_prediction_tokens\": 0\n          }\n        }\n      },\n      \"tool_call_chunks\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"load_skill\",\n          \"args\": \"{\\\"skillName\\\": \\\"retrieval-protocol\\\"}\",\n          \"id\": \"call_zxs31OjxSYsNsT3PSwozW9FU\",\n          \"index\": 0,\n          \"type\": \"tool_call_chunk\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"load_skill\",\n          \"args\": \"{\\\"skillName\\\": \\\"output-contract\\\"}\",\n          \"id\": \"call_fIxkLj7w5pbJUDvFyWl5W2is\",\n          \"index\": 1,\n          \"type\": \"tool_call_chunk\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"tool_calls\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"load_skill\",\n          \"args\": {\n            \"skillName\": \"retrieval-protocol\"\n          },\n          \"id\": \"call_zxs31OjxSYsNsT3PSwozW9FU\",\n          \"type\": \"tool_call\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"load_skill\",\n          \"args\": {\n            \"skillName\": \"output-contract\"\n          },\n          \"id\": \"call_fIxkLj7w5pbJUDvFyWl5W2is\",\n          \"type\": \"tool_call\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"id\": \"chatcmpl-DGsoy5Q3y3Tn3VDVJLar5hvYA8hbY\",\n      \"usage_metadata\": {\n        \"input_tokens\": 469,\n        \"output_tokens\": 53,\n        \"total_tokens\": 522,\n        \"input_token_details\": {\n          \"audio\": 0,\n          \"cache_read\": 0\n        },\n        \"output_token_details\": {\n          \"audio\": 0,\n          \"reasoning\": 0\n        }\n      },\n      \"invalid_tool_calls\": [],\n      \"name\": \"ELILEAI_Orchestrator_Agent\",\n      \"type\": \"ai\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"status\": \"success\",\n      \"content\": \"Loaded skill: retrieval-protocol\\n\\n---\\nname: retrieval-protocol\\ndescription: Use when answering questions that require grounding in source material or structured reasoning.\\n---\\n\\n# retrieval-protocol\\n\\n## Overview\\nThis skill defines a structured approach to reasoning through questions using available knowledge and sources.\\n\\n## When to Use\\n- Any question requiring factual grounding or policy/guideline reasoning\\n- \\\"Is this eligible?\\\", \\\"What is required?\\\", or \\\"How does X work?\\\" questions\\n\\n## Protocol\\n\\n### Step 1 — Classify the request\\nDetermine what type of question this is and what sources would be relevant.\\n\\n### Step 2 — Decompose into concepts\\nBreak the question into smaller parts. Reason about each separately.\\n\\n### Step 3 — Reason from sources\\nGround your answer in available knowledge. If you lack sufficient evidence, say so clearly.\\n\\n### Step 4 — Determine missing information\\nIf critical details are missing that would change the answer, ask targeted clarifying questions (up to 4).\\n\\n### Step 5 — Answer\\nProvide a direct, well-supported answer. If the answer is \\\"No\\\", explain what would need to change.\\n\",\n      \"tool_call_id\": \"call_zxs31OjxSYsNsT3PSwozW9FU\",\n      \"name\": \"load_skill\",\n      \"metadata\": {},\n      \"additional_kwargs\": {},\n      \"response_metadata\": {},\n      \"id\": \"8f6dd395-b9d6-4767-82f2-36935096945e\",\n      \"type\": \"tool\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"status\": \"success\",\n      \"content\": \"Loaded skill: output-contract\\n\\n---\\nname: output-contract\\ndescription: Use when producing a final response — defines strict response formats and ensures the agent never mixes answering with asking for more information.\\n---\\n\\n# output-contract\\n\\n## Overview\\nThis skill defines the response contract for the orchestrator agent so outputs are consistent and actionable.\\n\\n## When to Use\\n- Any time the agent is about to produce a final answer\\n- Any time the agent is about to ask clarifying questions\\n\\n## Output — choose exactly ONE path\\n\\n### If you CAN answer:\\n- Lead with the answer directly (Yes / No / a specific value / a short summary)\\n- Support with reasoning or evidence as needed\\n- Do NOT ask follow-up questions after providing an answer\\n\\n### If you CANNOT answer (missing critical info):\\n- First line: **\\\"I cannot answer until I have some more information\\\"**\\n- Then ask up to 4 targeted clarifying questions — keep them simple and direct\\n- Do NOT provide a partial answer alongside questions\\n\\n### If technical issues prevent answering:\\n- First line: **\\\"I cannot answer that at this time due to technical constraints\\\"**\\n\\n## Style Rules\\n- Be concise and direct\\n- Lead with what the user needs to know or do\\n- Use markdown for structure when the response is complex\\n- Never mix modes (answer + questions in the same response)\\n\",\n      \"tool_call_id\": \"call_fIxkLj7w5pbJUDvFyWl5W2is\",\n      \"name\": \"load_skill\",\n      \"metadata\": {},\n      \"additional_kwargs\": {},\n      \"response_metadata\": {},\n      \"id\": \"6e28d074-5e00-4de5-b6c9-64bddcf8fadc\",\n      \"type\": \"tool\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"content\": \"Okay, I will reply with one short sentence only.\",\n      \"additional_kwargs\": {},\n      \"response_metadata\": {\n        \"model_provider\": \"openai\",\n        \"usage\": {\n          \"prompt_tokens\": 1129,\n          \"completion_tokens\": 14,\n          \"total_tokens\": 1143,\n          \"prompt_tokens_details\": {\n            \"cached_tokens\": 0,\n            \"audio_tokens\": 0\n          },\n          \"completion_tokens_details\": {\n            \"reasoning_tokens\": 0,\n            \"audio_tokens\": 0,\n            \"accepted_prediction_tokens\": 0,\n            \"rejected_prediction_tokens\": 0\n          }\n        }\n      },\n      \"tool_call_chunks\": [],\n      \"tool_calls\": [],\n      \"id\": \"chatcmpl-DGsozpkFNbQdrV9Zd8oYiQPswsWSR\",\n      \"usage_metadata\": {\n        \"input_tokens\": 1129,\n        \"output_tokens\": 14,\n        \"total_tokens\": 1143,\n        \"input_token_details\": {\n          \"audio\": 0,\n          \"cache_read\": 0\n        },\n        \"output_token_details\": {\n          \"audio\": 0,\n          \"reasoning\": 0\n        }\n      },\n      \"invalid_tool_calls\": [],\n      \"name\": \"ELILEAI_Orchestrator_Agent\",\n      \"type\": \"ai\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"
